cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the challenges of learning compositional solutions in various domains, including language modeling, visual question answering, and machine comprehension. These domains are typically associated with the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
